  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view of Alcatraz Island and the Golden Gate Bridge at sunset. The sky is ablaze with vibrant orange and yellow hues, creating dramatic, radiating light beams. The Golden Gate Bridge is silhouetted against the glowing horizon, with a gentle fog layer partially obscuring its lower structures. Alcatraz Island stands prominently in the foreground, a dark, imposing shape against the shimmering water. The sea is calm with slight ripples, reflecting the warm colors of the sky. Distant landmasses are visible, adding depth to the expansive landscape.",
